short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Improves readability of Logeion LSJ entries

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds a small amount of custom CSS to LSJ entries on Logeion (https://logeion.uchicago.edu) in order to make the entries more readable and easier to use.
